## Coordination matrix (Muster)

| Role | Owns | Hands off to |
|------|------|--------------|
| **PM** | Backlog, AC, `product-brief`, prioritization | Architect: `BLOCKED` без стека; Developer: `READY` |
| **IT-Architect** | Stack, ADR, `architecture.md`, unblock `BLOCKED` | PM: обновить queue; Developer: implement |
| **Developer** | Code, migrations, APIs per AC | Architect: новый `BLOCKED`; QA: verify |
| **UI/UX** | Tokens, layouts, a11y | Architect: только если data model влияет на UX flows |
| **QA** | AC verification, `qa-checklist` | PM + Human: sign-off |

**Parallel agents:** разные task ID; Architect не трогает `IN_PROGRESS` Developer без Human.

